reviewText: There seems to be some confusion over Tai Seng's numerous Asian model releases.  They are typically rather ingenuous (by American standards) nude  "pictorials" of attractive, mostly Japanese, models.  Some of the  "models" are actually porn stars - which is not such a bad thing  in Japan, where some of the better porn stars do gameshows and are the  featured voices of popular anime characters.  Ultimately, the DVDs are  innocuous and really quite innocent.  But the amount of nudity they exhibit  does not make them innocent enough to warrant a PG rating.
